94
00:05:22,180 --> 00:05:24,234
You see that the icicle, respectively:

95
00:05:24,234 --> 00:05:28,910
the escape velocity
from Jupiter is very, very large;

96
00:05:28,910 --> 00:05:31,047
the one from Mercury is very small.

97
00:05:31,047 --> 00:05:33,418
And this is an interesting graph
because it shows

98
00:05:33,418 --> 00:05:35,528
that from the surface of the planet,

99
00:05:35,528 --> 00:05:37,622
in order to escape the solar system

100
00:05:37,622 --> 00:05:41,544
you have, first of all,
