138
00:07:47,033 --> 00:07:49,577
and you're also going to reach infinity

139
00:07:49,577 --> 00:07:51,311
after a very long time at zero velocity.

140
00:07:51,311 --> 00:07:54,001
That's, again, a principle.

141
00:07:54,001 --> 00:07:56,217
It's not something
