145
00:08:04,202 --> 00:08:08,497
If you have less than 11.2 km/s,
like 10 km/s,

146
00:08:08,497 --> 00:08:10,713
you come on an elliptical orbit.

147
00:08:10,713 --> 00:08:14,298
So, again, whatever
the direction of escape

148
00:08:14,298 --> 00:08:18,425
from a distance <i>r</i>
to the center of the Earth,

149
00:08:18,425 --> 00:08:20,411
if you have the escape velocity

150
00:08:20,411 --> 00:08:22,668
you are eventually
going to get to infinity

151
00:08:22,668 --> 00:08:25,590
or to a large distance,
at a zero velocity.
